pasti tak datang.</font>

12
00:01:01,945 --> 00:01:03,714
<font color=#FFFF00>Tapi kenapa kalian duduk
bersebelahan.</font>

13
00:01:04,714 --> 00:01:06,244
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku malas saja lihat
mukanya.</font>

14
00:01:07,945 --> 00:01:08,945
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa katamu?</font>

15
00:01:10,154 --> 00:01:12,085
<font color=#FFFF00>Kalian tahu sendiri, aku...</font>

16
00:01:13,255 --> 00:01:15,824
<font color=#FFFF00>...ada yang ingin
kukatakan ke kalian.</font>

17
00:01:16,025 --> 00:01:17,195
