18
00:01:22,025 --> 00:01:25,094
<font color=#FFFF00>Pokoknya harus kukatakan
ke kalian.</font>

19
00:01:27,505 --> 00:01:29,535
<font color=#FFFF00>Jadi begini.</font>

20
00:01:29,975 --> 00:01:32,005
<font color=#FFFF00>Kita minum dulu.</font>

21
00:01:34,205 --> 00:01:36,244
<font color=#FFFF00>Apaan? Apa ada masalah?</font>

22
00:01:36,404 --> 00:01:37,744
<font color=#FFFF00>Apaan? Aku jadi gelisah.</font>

23
00:01:38,175 --> 00:01:39,344
<font color=#FFFF00>Ada apa?</font>

24
00:01:41,484 --> 00:01:42,844
<font color=#FFFF00>Begini...</font>

25
00:01:47,755 --> 00:01:48,824
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku...</font>

26
00:01:50,395 --> 00:01:52,420
<font color=#FFFF00>Setelah kita mengaplikasikan
SEO (pengoptimalan...</font>

27
00:01:52,445 --> 00:01:54,089
<font color=#FFFF00>...situs), barulah kita
bahas pemasukan.</font>

28
00:01:54,824 --> 00:01:56,764
<font color=#FFFF00>Ada lagi yang mau ditambahkan?</font>

29
00:01:56,764 --> 00:01:58,594
<font color=#FFFF00><i>[Katakan pada kenalan]</i></font>

30
00:02:02,634 --> 00:02:04,104
<font color=#FFFF00>Ya?</font>

31
00:02:04,205 --> 00:02:05,775
<font color=#FFFF00>Sewaktu makan malam
tim terakhir itu...,</font>

32
00:02:05,835 --> 00:02:09,932
<font color=#FFFF00>...berapa dari kalian yang main taruhan
soal keseksualitasku?</font>

33
00:02:12,444 --> 00:02:14,714
<font color=#FFFF00>Taruhan apa?</font>

34
00:02:14,714 --> 00:02:16,714
<font color=#FFFF00>Kenapa pula kami
main begituan?</font>

35
00:02:16,885 --> 00:02:18,184
<font color=#FFFF00>Kita mana main taruhan
seperti itu.</font>

36
00:02:18,515 --> 00:02:20,784
<font color=#FFFF00>Memangnya kami tak punya
kerjaan, apa?</font>

37
00:02:21,485 --> 00:02:22,885
<font color=#FFFF00>Dasar, tak masuk akal
sekali.</font>

38
00:02:23,555 --> 00:02:26,694
<font color=#FFFF00>Siapa yang taruhan kalau
aku homo?</font>

39
00:02:30,164 --> 00:02:31,395
<font color=#FFFF00>Yang taruhan kalau
aku normal?</font>

40
00:02:33,664 --> 00:02:34,904
<font color=#FFFF00>Kalau aseksual?</font>

41
00:02:37,974 --> 00:02:39,434
<font color=#FFFF00>Selamat, Bo Mi-nim.</font>

42
00:02:41,874 --> 00:02:44,244
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku mau menikah.</font>

43
00:02:44,874 --> 00:02:45,944
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa?</font>

44
00:02:47,545 --> 00:02:48,944
<font color=#FFFF00>Tn. Nam?</font>

45
00:02:50,055 --> 00:02:51,485
<font color=#FFFF00>Dia mau apa?</font>

46
00:02:51,914 --> 00:02:53,485
<font color=#FFFF00>Menikah./
Menikah?</font>

47
00:02:55,485 --> 00:02:56,955
<font color=#FFFF00>Bayar taruhannya. 50 ribu.</font>

48
00:02:58,395 --> 00:03:00,464
<font color=#FFFF00>Tn. Nam, bisa kita bicara sebentar?</font>

49
00:03:00,895 --> 00:03:02,925
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa mungkin kau marah...</font>

50
00:03:02,925 --> 00:03:05,934
<font color=#FFFF00>...karena kami taruhan?</font>

51
00:03:06,034 --> 00:03:07,534
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa karena itu?</font>

52
00:03:07,705 --> 00:03:09,164
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa kau sudah bayar 50 ribu?</font>

53
00:03:11,374 --> 00:03:14,075
<font color=#FFFF00>Hei. Kau mau menikah?
Menikah sungguhan?</font>

54
00:03:14,205 --> 00:03:16,575
<font color=#FFFF00>Marriage? Wedding? Pemberkatan nikah?</font>

55
00:03:17,115 --> 00:03:18,145
<font color=#FFFF00>Ya.</font>

56
00:03:18,874 --> 00:03:20,414
<font color=#FFFF00>Sama wanita?</font>

57
00:03:20,615 --> 00:03:21,645
<font color=#FFFF00>Ya.</font>

58
00:03:21,844 --> 00:03:23,714
<font color=#FFFF00>Jangan buat aku tertawa!
Mana bisa kau menikah?</font>

59
00:03:23,714 --> 00:03:25,885
<font color=#FFFF00>Seorang aseksual mana
bisa menikah.</font>

60
00:03:25,885 --> 00:03:28,124
<font color=#FFFF00>Pikirmu aku percaya?
Pasti pernikahan pura-pura, 'kan?</font>

61
00:03:28,254 --> 00:03:31,754
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau boleh saja bohongi orang,
tapi aku tidak.</font>

62
00:03:31,994 --> 00:03:33,124
<font color=#FFFF00>Dia cantik.</font>

63
00:03:35,564 --> 00:03:37,295
<font color=#FFFF00>Cantik?/
Ya.</font>

64
00:03:41,434 --> 00:03:42,664
<font color=#FFFF00>Sangat.</font>

65
00:03:47,275 --> 00:03:48,904
<font color=#FFFF00>Se Hee memang jatuh cinta.</font>

66
00:03:50,145 --> 00:03:52,545
<font color=#FFFF00>Se Hee akhirnya jatuh cinta!</font>

67
00:03:55,385 --> 00:03:58,455
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau mau.../
Menikah?</font>

68
00:03:59,015 --> 00:04:00,224
<font color=#FFFF00>Sama majikan rumah?</font>

69
00:04:03,425 --> 00:04:04,555
<font color=#FFFF00>Kalian kaget, ya?</font>

70
00:04:14,335 --> 00:04:15,735
<font color=#FFFF00>Kalian kapan pacarannya?</font>

71
00:04:16,435 --> 00:04:17,534
<font color=#FFFF00>Pacaran?</font>

72
00:04:19,674 --> 00:04:23,005
<font color=#FFFF00>Kami cuma pacaran
kurang lebih sebulan atau 2 bulan.</font>

73
00:04:23,075 --> 00:04:26,044
<font color=#FFFF00>Jadi maksudnya sejak kau pindah
ke rumah itu, kalian pacaran?</font>

74
00:04:27,085 --> 00:04:28,414
<font color=#FFFF00>Begitulah.</font>

75
00:04:28,414 --> 00:04:29,784
<font color=#FFFF00>Sejak darisitu kalian pacaran?</font>

76
00:04:29,914 --> 00:04:31,114
<font color=#FFFF00>Ya.</font>

77
00:04:31,114 --> 00:04:32,654
<font color=#FFFF00>Tapi kenapa kau tak
cerita?</font>

78
00:04:32,755 --> 00:04:35,025
<font color=#FFFF00>Katamu, tak ada apa-apa
di antara kalian berdua.</font>

79
00:04:35,125 --> 00:04:36,825
<font color=#FFFF00>Ya, 'kan?</font>

80
00:04:37,424 --> 00:04:40,325
<font color=#FFFF00>Ya. Awalnya aneh, waktu kau
menyangkal.</font>

81
00:04:42,025 --> 00:04:45,294
<font color=#FFFF00>Itu karena kami baru pacaran.</font>

82
00:04:45,695 --> 00:04:48,604
<font color=#FFFF00>Malu mau cerita-cerita
sama kalian.</font>

83
00:04:48,604 --> 00:04:50,575
<font color=#FFFF00>Tapi kalian mau menikah secepat ini?</font>

84
00:04:50,935 --> 00:04:52,674
<font color=#FFFF00>Ya.</font>

85
00:04:54,104 --> 00:04:58,015
<font color=#FFFF00>Banyak orang menikah
cepat-cepat.</font>

86
00:04:58,015 --> 00:04:59,645
<font color=#FFFF00>Itu 'kan orang lain.</font>

87
00:04:59,645 --> 00:05:01,484
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau bukan kebanyakan orang.
Kau itu Ji Ho.</font>

88
00:05:02,885 --> 00:05:04,484
<font color=#FFFF00>Memang aku kenapa?</font>

89
00:05:04,484 --> 00:05:07,255
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau itu butuh berbulan-bulan
buat dekat sama orang.</font>

90
00:05:07,255 --> 00:05:10,354
<font color=#FFFF00>Aneh kau menikah secepat ini.</font>

91
00:05:10,354 --> 00:05:11,455
<font color=#FFFF00>Aneh, 'kan?</font>

92
00:05:13,224 --> 00:05:15,094
<font color=#FFFF00>Suatu hubungan cinta...</font>

93
00:05:15,364 --> 00:05:18,594
<font color=#FFFF00>...tak melulu mengandalkan
waktu mereka saling mengenal.</font>

94
00:05:20,205 --> 00:05:21,304
<font color=#FFFF00>Jadi...</font>

95
00:05:22,464 --> 00:05:24,234
<font color=#FFFF00>Walaupun kami baru kenal...,</font>

96
00:05:24,335 --> 00:05:27,044
<font color=#FFFF00>...kurasa dia orang yang kubutuhkan
dalam hidupku...</font>

97
00:05:27,044 --> 00:05:28,145
<font color=#FFFF00>Butuh?</font>

98
00:05:32,614 --> 00:05:36,185
<font color=#FFFF00>Mungkin kedengarannya aneh
kalau kubilang aku butuh dia...</font>

99
00:05:36,185 --> 00:05:37,755
<font color=#FFFF00>...padahal 'kan dia orang
(benda hidup)...</font>

100
00:05:38,085 --> 00:05:40,755
<font color=#FFFF00>Jadi maksudku...</font>

101
00:05:43,325 --> 00:05:45,695
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku paham. Kenapa kau menikah.</font>

102
00:05:46,424 --> 00:05:47,525
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa?</font>

103
00:05:48,265 --> 00:05:49,395
<font color=#FFFF00>Ji Ho, kau...</font>

104
00:05:53,234 --> 00:05:54,604
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau jatuh cinta pada pandangan pertama, ya?</font>

105
00:05:58,705 --> 00:06:00,844
<font color=#FFFF00>Sewaktu pertama bertemu dia,
kau langsung jatuh cinta, 'kan?</font>

106
00:06:00,844 --> 00:06:04,044
<font color=#FFFF00>Kenapa, di film sama drama juga banyak
seperti itu. Seperti ada percikan, 'kan?</font>

107
00:06:04,844 --> 00:06:06,344
<font color=#FFFF00>Ya. Betul.</font>

108
00:06:06,945 --> 00:06:08,015
<font color=#FFFF00>Sungguh?</font>

109
00:06:09,414 --> 00:06:12,614
<font color=#FFFF00>Yah, terjadi begitu saja.</font>

110
00:06:12,685 --> 00:06:17,054
<font color=#FFFF00>Sewaktu aku bertemu dia,
mataku langsung bersinar.</font>

111
00:06:18,354 --> 00:06:21,325
<font color=#FFFF00>Makanya kau mau menikah
secepat ini.</font>

112
00:06:22,195 --> 00:06:23,294
<font color=#FFFF00>Ya.</font>

113
00:06:25,364 --> 00:06:27,464
<font color=#FFFF00>Kurasa ini takdir.</font>

114
00:06:28,765 --> 00:06:30,904
<font color=#FFFF00>Takdir?/
Bagaimana ini?</font>

115
00:06:41,315 --> 00:06:43,284
<font color=#FFFF00>Kurasa ini takdir.</font>

116
00:06:45,185 --> 00:06:46,455
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku pasti sudah gila.</font>

117
00:06:47,585 --> 00:06:48,854
<font color=#FFFF00>Setelah menulis beberapa drama...,</font>

118
00:06:49,255 --> 00:06:51,455
<font color=#FFFF00>...aku makin mahir saja
berakting.</font>

119
00:07:10,214 --> 00:07:12,745
<font color=#FFFF00>Ayo. Lewat situ.</font>

120
00:07:18,815 --> 00:07:21,724
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau sudah kasih tahu
rekan kerjamu?</font>

121
00:07:21,825 --> 00:07:24,455
<font color=#FFFF00>Ya. Tadi kami rapat...,</font>

122
00:07:24,554 --> 00:07:26,395
<font color=#FFFF00>...jadi aku sekalian
kasih tahu mereka.</font>

123
00:07:28,025 --> 00:07:31,094
<font color=#FFFF00>Kalau soal rekan kerjamu
yang kelihatannya tak percaya?</font>

124
00:07:31,094 --> 00:07:33,205
<font color=#FFFF00>Ternyata tanggapannya
tak terlalu berlebihan.</font>

125
00:07:33,765 --> 00:07:36,534
<font color=#FFFF00>Karena aku tadi memanfaatkan
sifat alami psikologi pria.</font>

126
00:07:36,804 --> 00:07:37,904
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa?</font>

127
00:07:39,335 --> 00:07:40,404
<font color=#FFFF00>Kalau kau?</font>

128
00:07:40,404 --> 00:07:44,075
<font color=#FFFF00>Mereka 'kan sahabatmu dari kecil,
kau pasti khawatir.</font>

129
00:07:45,375 --> 00:07:47,645
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku juga sudah kasih tahu mereka.</font>

130
00:07:47,745 --> 00:07:49,585
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau pakai taktik macam apa?</font>

131
00:07:49,585 --> 00:07:51,885
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku bilang ke mereka
kalau ini tak...</font>

132
00:07:52,755 --> 00:07:53,854
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa?</font>

133
00:07:54,525 --> 00:07:57,955
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku bilang ke mereka...
kalau aku beruntung.</font>

134
00:07:58,154 --> 00:08:00,265
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku pakai metode storytelling.</font>

135
00:08:00,364 --> 00:08:03,094
<font color=#FFFF00>Tak kusangka jadi penulis drama,
ada untungnya juga seperti ini.</font>

136
00:08:03,094 --> 00:08:04,294
<font color=#FFFF00>Begitu rupanya.</font>

137
00:08:10,505 --> 00:08:12,174
<font color=#FFFF00><i>[Nam Hee Bong]</i></font>

138
00:08:15,205 --> 00:08:17,275
<font color=#FFFF00>Jadi, kita masuk sekarang?</font>

139
00:08:20,745 --> 00:08:23,885
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau tak apa?</font>

140
00:08:25,255 --> 00:08:28,025
<font color=#FFFF00>Ya. Aku akan berusaha terbaik.</font>

141
00:08:29,955 --> 00:08:32,454
<font color=#FFFF00>Ibumu pasti sudah menonton
dramaku...,</font>

142
00:08:33,125 --> 00:08:34,895
<font color=#FFFF00>...jadi kurasa takkan ada masalah.</font>

143
00:08:36,324 --> 00:08:37,465
<font color=#FFFF00>Adapun, ayahmu...</font>

144
00:08:37,465 --> 00:08:42,164
<font color=#FFFF00>Tak perlu hiraukan dia.</font>

145
00:08:59,015 --> 00:09:01,584
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Ibunya si majikan rumah,
Cho Myeong Ja.</i></font>

146
00:09:02,225 --> 00:09:03,924
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Dia berasal dari Jongno,
di Seoul.</i></font>

147
00:09:04,054 --> 00:09:05,755
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Dia lahir tahun 1955.</i></font>

148
00:09:08,664 --> 00:09:11,735
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Dia ingin dianggap sebagai
istri baik dan ibu yang bijak.</i></font>

149
00:09:11,735 --> 00:09:12,735
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Dia ibu-ibu rumah tangga.</i></font>

150
00:09:14,834 --> 00:09:15,934
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau sudah sampai?</font>

151
00:09:16,034 --> 00:09:17,334
<font color=#FFFF00>Kabar Ibu baik?/
Ya.</font>

152
00:09:17,334 --> 00:09:20,245
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Dia ingin masalah pernikahan
anaknya cepat teratasi...</i></font>

153
00:09:20,375 --> 00:09:22,544
<font color=#FFFF00><i>...agar keluarganya bisa tenang.</i></font>

154
00:09:22,704 --> 00:09:25,574
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Dia tipikal ibu yang selalu bertindak
apa yang menurutnya aman.</i></font>

155
00:09:25,574 --> 00:09:27,745
<font color=#FFFF00>Ini Ji Ho yang kuceritakan.</font>

156
00:09:28,414 --> 00:09:30,355
<font color=#FFFF00>Selamat pagi./
Kau sudah datang.</font>

157
00:09:30,615 --> 00:09:33,424
<font color=#FFFF00>Susah, ya, kesini?/
Tidak juga.</font>

158
00:09:33,584 --> 00:09:36,355
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku tak yakin apa Ibu suka ini...</font>

159
00:09:36,355 --> 00:09:38,194
<font color=#FFFF00>Ya, ampun.</font>

160
00:09:38,255 --> 00:09:40,395
<font color=#FFFF00>Mana ada wanita yang
benci bunga.</font>

161
00:09:42,564 --> 00:09:44,265
<font color=#FFFF00>Baunya enak.</font>

162
00:09:44,595 --> 00:09:47,005
<font color=#FFFF00>Sudah lama aku tak
dapat karangan bunga.</font>

163
00:09:47,064 --> 00:09:48,865
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Aku pakarnya menangani
karakter orang seperti dia.</i></font>

164
00:09:49,265 --> 00:09:51,304
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Untunglah aku pernah bekerja cukup
lama menulis drama harian.</i></font>

165
00:09:51,434 --> 00:09:54,704
<font color=#FFFF00>Ayahmu lagi liburan
sama temannya.</font>

166
00:09:54,704 --> 00:09:56,245
<font color=#FFFF00>Dia sebentar lagi pulang
dari bandara.</font>

167
00:09:56,745 --> 00:09:58,215
<font color=#FFFF00>Duduklah./
Ya.</font>

168
00:10:08,225 --> 00:10:10,154
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Ayah si majikan rumah, Nam Hee Bong.</i></font>

169
00:10:11,395 --> 00:10:14,664
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Dia guru kewarganegaraan
selama 30 tahun...</i></font>

170
00:10:14,924 --> 00:10:16,172
<font color=#FFFF00><i>...sebelum akhirnya dia
pensiunan tahun lalu...</i></font>

171
00:10:16,197 --> 00:10:17,358
<font color=#FFFF00><i>...setelah melayani menjadi
kepala sekolah.</i></font>

172
00:10:18,265 --> 00:10:19,495
<font color=#FFFF00><i>[Hormati gurumu, sayangi muridmu]</i></font>

173
00:10:19,495 --> 00:10:21,505
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Dia karakter orang berpendidikan.</i></font>

174
00:10:22,904 --> 00:10:24,704
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Aku pakarnya menangani
orang-orang seperti ini.</i></font>

175
00:10:25,135 --> 00:10:27,775
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Kurasa ini bakal semudah
yang kubayangkan...</i></font>

176
00:10:29,975 --> 00:10:31,044
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau sudah sampai?</font>

177
00:10:49,424 --> 00:10:53,404
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku juga tak tahu. Kukira
itu karena kau cuma penyewa.</font>

178
00:10:53,704 --> 00:10:55,019
<font color=#FFFF00>Pasangan memang wajar...</font>

179
00:10:55,044 --> 00:10:56,358
<font color=#FFFF00>...saling berkunjung ke
rumah masing-masing.</font>

180
00:10:57,034 --> 00:10:58,875
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau pikir kami akan
salah paham?</font>

181
00:10:59,475 --> 00:11:00,605
<font color=#FFFF00>Ya, 'kan, sayang?</font>

182
