202
00:12:01,204 --> 00:12:03,404
<font color=#FFFF00>Pertanyaan macam apa itu?</font>

203
00:12:03,605 --> 00:12:05,174
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau itu 'kan lulusan
universitas bagus.</font>

204
00:12:05,375 --> 00:12:08,275
<font color=#FFFF00>Kalau kau penulis, kau pasti
