205
00:12:08,275 --> 00:12:10,314
<font color=#FFFF00>Lantas kenapa mendadak
kau ingin menikah?</font>

206
00:12:10,814 --> 00:12:11,875
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau pun sampai berhenti
