213
00:12:33,904 --> 00:12:35,605
<font color=#FFFF00>Bukankah belakangan ini, pasangan...</font>

214
00:12:35,804 --> 00:12:38,105
<font color=#FFFF00>...ada panggilan sayangnya?/
