230
00:13:52,044 --> 00:13:53,485
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau cukup telat makannya.</font>

231
00:13:53,715 --> 00:13:55,745
<font color=#FFFF00>Ya, aku tadi kesiangan.</font>

232
00:13:58,054 --> 00:14:00,684
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku pasti agak gelisah waktu
