233
00:14:02,084 --> 00:14:04,395
<font color=#FFFF00>Ya, kau pasti panik waktu itu.</font>

234
00:14:04,924 --> 00:14:06,824
<font color=#FFFF00>Ya, kurasa.</font>

235
00:14:08,294 --> 00:14:09,965
<font color=#FFFF00>Kalau kau sepanik itu...,</font>

236
00:14:10,294 --> 00:14:11,465
<font color=#FFFF00>...bagaimana bisa kau
