237
00:14:12,064 --> 00:14:13,135
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa?</font>

238
00:14:13,164 --> 00:14:14,404
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Oppa...</i></font>

239
00:14:16,635 --> 00:14:18,704
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku mencintainya.</font>

240
00:14:20,345 --> 00:14:23,414
<font color=#FFFF00>Bukannya kalimat itu dari
naskah?</font>

241
00:14:29,314 --> 00:14:31,914
<font color=#FFFF00>Karena pilihan katamu yang berani itu,
aku agak kaget.</font>

242
00:14:31,914 --> 00:14:33,015
<font color=#FFFF00>Ya...</font>

243
00:14:33,755 --> 00:14:36,694
<font color=#FFFF00>Karena kupikir ayahmu tipe orang...</font>

244
00:14:37,495 --> 00:14:39,694
<font color=#FFFF00>...yang blak-blakan.</font>

245
00:14:39,995 --> 00:14:43,334
<font color=#FFFF00>Ya. Tapi itu agak tak terduga.</font>

246
00:14:44,064 --> 00:14:46,064
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku pun heran itu
