252
00:15:05,184 --> 00:15:08,525
<font color=#FFFF00>Dalam situasi seperti itu,
tak ada yang namanya blak-blakan...</font>

253
00:15:09,355 --> 00:15:12,194
<font color=#FFFF00>...dibanding berkata aku mencintaimu.</font>

254
00:15:13,625 --> 00:15:14,664
<font color=#FFFF00>Benar juga.</font>

255
00:15:14,865 --> 00:15:16,995
<font color=#FFFF00>Itu juga kata yang mudah
diucapkan.</font>

256
00:15:21,635 --> 00:15:24,005
<font color=#FFFF00>Sekarang, kita hanya perlu saling
bertemu orang tua kita besok.</font>

257
00:15:25,534 --> 00:15:28,875
<font color=#FFFF00>Ya. Jadi setelah itu,
prosesnya selesai?</font>

258
00:15:29,275 --> 00:15:31,275
<font color=#FFFF00>Ya, kalau tak ada kendala.</font>

259
00:15:31,914 --> 00:15:33,145
<font color=#FFFF00>Kuyakin pasti tak ada.</font>

260
00:15:35,184 --> 00:15:36,245
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku olahraga dulu.</font>

261
00:15:37,784 --> 00:15:38,985
<font color=#FFFF00>Dah.</font>

262
00:15:52,135 --> 00:15:55,465
<font color=#FFFF00><i>[Apa kalian pada sibuk?
Haruskah kita makan malam bersama?]</i></font>

263
00:16:02,404 --> 00:16:03,715
<font color=#FFFF00>Cantiknya.</font>

264
00:16:06,615 --> 00:16:07,645
<font color=#FFFF00>Apanya?</font>

265
00:16:08,684 --> 00:16:10,115
<font color=#FFFF00>Debu halusnya.</font>

266
00:16:12,715 --> 00:16:16,025
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku seperti orang gila, ya?/
