267
00:16:17,054 --> 00:16:18,255
<font color=#FFFF00>Lebih gila dari Ji Ho?</font>

268
00:16:20,265 --> 00:16:21,465
<font color=#FFFF00>Tidak.</font>

269
00:16:24,395 --> 00:16:26,804
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Soo Ji, si Ho Rang tak apa?</i></font>

270
00:16:27,164 --> 00:16:30,034
<font color=#FFFF00>Dia bilang apa?
