274
00:16:45,054 --> 00:16:47,255
<font color=#FFFF00>Tidak, cuma sedikit.</font>

275
00:17:05,304 --> 00:17:08,505
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Ji Ho, waktu kau bertemu orang
