276
00:17:08,505 --> 00:17:09,544
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Oke?</i></font>

277
00:17:12,215 --> 00:17:14,485
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Aku tahu ini kedengarannya aneh...,</i></font>

278
00:17:15,084 --> 00:17:20,970
<font color=#FFFF00><i>...tapi maaf aku harus menikah
di saat seperti ini.</i></font>

279
00:17:24,755 --> 00:17:26,354
<font color=#FFFF00>Sudah kuduga.</font>

280
00:17:28,695 --> 00:17:31,394
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Jadi merasa tak enaknya
sampai hari ini saja, ya?</i></font>

281
00:17:36,735 --> 00:17:39,874
<font color=#FFFF00>Kenapa dia merasa tak enak?
Dia 'kan bukannya mau menikah sama suamiku.</font>

282
00:17:40,175 --> 00:17:41,544
<font color=#FFFF00>Polos sekali dia ini.</font>

283
00:17:44,044 --> 00:17:46,215
<font color=#FFFF00>Hei, kau juga belum pernah
melihatnya, 'kan?</font>

284
00:17:46,374 --> 00:17:47,544
<font color=#FFFF00>Siapa?</font>

285
00:17:47,985 --> 00:17:49,084
<font color=#FFFF00>Suaminya Ji Ho.</font>

286
00:17:49,544 --> 00:17:50,784
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau juga tak tahu
apa-apa, 'kan?</font>

287
00:17:51,455 --> 00:17:52,715
<font color=#FFFF00>Mana aku tahu begituan?</font>

288
00:17:54,824 --> 00:17:57,425
<font color=#FFFF00>Sebelum mereka menikah, kita
harus tahu semuanya tentang pria itu.</font>

289
00:17:58,155 --> 00:18:00,064
<font color=#FFFF00>Si polos Ji Ho itu tak menikah
sama penipu, 'kan?</font>

290
00:18:00,294 --> 00:18:02,294
<font color=#FFFF00>Kalau Won Seok pulang,
tanya saja dia.</font>

291
00:18:03,064 --> 00:18:05,094
<font color=#FFFF00>Dia pasti tahu banyak tentangnya.</font>

292
00:18:08,364 --> 00:18:09,405
<font color=#FFFF00>Kenapa?</font>

293
00:18:10,275 --> 00:18:11,775
<font color=#FFFF00>Kalian masih bertengkar?</font>

294
00:18:14,205 --> 00:18:17,475
<font color=#FFFF00>Sudah lima hari dia
