295
00:18:20,915 --> 00:18:22,284
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau tak bisa kembalikan sofanya?</font>

296
00:18:22,685 --> 00:18:25,614
<font color=#FFFF00>Tak bisa.</font>

297
00:18:32,124 --> 00:18:33,364
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau tak pulang?</font>

298
00:18:33,425 --> 00:18:36,394
<font color=#FFFF00>Sudah tiga hari ini, aku minum
