299
00:18:36,634 --> 00:18:39,905
<font color=#FFFF00>Organku sepertinya mau meledak
rasanya.</font>

300
00:18:39,905 --> 00:18:43,005
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku bisa pulang kalau aku punya
