306
00:18:56,314 --> 00:18:59,314
<font color=#FFFF00>Makanya, kenapa pacarmu
itu jadi marah-marah?</font>

307
00:18:59,354 --> 00:19:01,624
<font color=#FFFF00>Padahal 'kan kau beli
sofa yang dia inginkan.</font>

308
00:19:01,624 --> 00:19:04,425
<font color=#FFFF00>Kalau bukan sofa, terus apa?</font>

309
00:19:05,394 --> 00:19:07,794
<font color=#FFFF00>Tak tahulah. Mana bisa
